<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <title>Registration Confirmation</title>
    <style>
        .email-container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            padding: 20px;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }
        .welcome-header {
            color: #2c3e50;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 20px 0;
        }
        .account-details {
            background-color: #f8f9fa;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .account-number {
            font-size: 20px;
            color: #3498db;
            font-weight: bold;
        }
        .status-pending {
            background-color: #fff3cd;
            border-left: 4px solid #ffc107;
            padding: 15px;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .next-steps {
            background-color: #e8f4f8;
            padding: 15px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="email-container">
        <h1 class="welcome-header">Welcome to Our Banking Service! üéâ</h1>
        
        <p>Dear {{firstName}} {{lastName}},</p>
        
        <p>Thank you for registering with us. Your account has been successfully created and is currently pending verification.</p>
        
        <div class="account-details">
            <h3>Your Account Details:</h3>
            <p>Name: {{firstName}} {{lastName}}</p>
            <p>Account Number: <span class="account-number">{{accountNumber}}</span></p>
            <p>Email: {{email}}</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="status-pending">
            <h3>‚è≥ Account Status: Pending Verification</h3>
            <p>Your account is currently under review by our team. This process typically takes 24-48 hours.</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="next-steps">
            <h3>What's Next?</h3>
            <ul>
                <li>Our team will verify your submitted documents</li>
                <li>You'll receive another email once your account is approved</li>
                <li>After approval, you can log in and start using your account</li>
            </ul>
        </div>
        
        <p>If you have any questions during this process, please don't hesitate to contact our support team.</p>
        
        <p>Best regards,<br>
        Your Banking Team</p>
        
        <hr>
        <p style="font-size: 12px; color: #666;">
            This is an automated message, please do not reply directly to this email.
            If you need assistance, please contact our support team.
        </p>
    </div>
</body>
</html> 